msgstr "免费方案：1 个投资组合、手动录入、基础图表。"

msgid "True returns"
msgstr "真实收益"

msgid ""
"Time-weighted and money-weighted performance computed with exact decimal "
"math."
msgstr "采用精确的十进制运算，计算时间加权和资金加权收益。"

msgid "Allocation & risk"
msgstr "配置与风险"

